First thing they should learn to be is a Honorable Nepali rather than a personnel of a party. And about the Song, its really a Honorable revolutionary Nepali song. Please let at least the  Nepalese sing songs, that's not hurting anyone, it hurts the ones who are involved in corruptions. The good ones should be happy with the song and should support the song. By the way, I have never belonged to any party and I voted Congress at provincial level and communist at national level and my thought was, the candidates were Honorable Nepali and would work for better Nepal irrespective of parties they got involved in. And I am from Pokhara and a doctor who actually never knew about state of Nepal and its parties before but always dreamt of a prosperous Nepal and me as a part of its contribution. Please don't take this otherwise but its my honest feeling. I am still hopeful for our future today and working hard from my side and are you from yours?
